## 9. Tally Routing Decision Tree

```
Source row examined (cols D, E):
│
├─ col D = "(OUTSOURCED)"     → insert below "OUTSOURCED" marker
├─ col D = "(DESIGN ONLY)"   → insert below "DESIGN; DESIGN ONLY ORDERS"
├─ col D = "(INSTALL)"        → insert below "INSTALL READY/DELIVERY/SHIPPING/INVOICING"
├─ col E = "No"               → insert below "COMING UP…"         (comingUpAdded++)
├─ col E = "Yes"              → insert below "DESIGN; PRODUCTION/ACTUAL ORDERS" (designAdded++)
├─ col E = "Approved"         → insert below "COMING UP…"         (comingUpAdded++)
├─ col A = ""                 → stop processing (end of data)
└─ else                       → skip row
```

For **Harmony/Gary tally** rows:
```
├─ col D = "(INV)"  → insert below "Harmony Brands INV Orders/FoF PO's"
├─ col D = "(COM)"  → insert below "COMING UP…"
├─ col A = ""       → stop processing
└─ else             → skip row
```

